  <h2>Quick Answer: When Do These Work Best?</h2>

  <div class="quickAnswerBox">
    <ul class="plainList">
      <li><strong>Best for simple setups:</strong> fixed hook-and-string systems.</li>
      <li><strong>Best for longer seasons:</strong> consider adjustable systems.</li>
